'''Israel''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in September 2018. Its default cities are the capital, Jerusalem, along with Bethlehem and Tel Aviv.

Although there is currently a real-life war between Israel and Hamas, no [[Death|deaths]] related to terrorist or battlefield attacks occur in the Bitlife version.
